text: Phindavele high school is a public school located in Dududu, south coast of KwaZulu Natal. It opened in 1978. The school enrolls about 1000 pupils. The school falls under quantile 3. It has no Internet access, library or laboratories. == References == Category:Schools in KwaZulu-Natal Category:Educational institutions established in 1978
title: Phindavele High School
